
I18nEditor
==========
A simple web based editor for editing .po files

Installation
------------
- install dIngle (not possible yet)
- install App::dingle
- use Build.PL to install dependencies
- use dingle to install site-lib and dingle-lib
- rename ENV.sh.sample to ENV.sh and load it
- start webserver with perl bin/i18nedit.pl
- have fun